propertyObj.description: Set parameter to true if you like to use custom error handling instead of standard error handling.
Maintain ProcessDirect end point of custom error handling flow in case of custom error handling instead of standard error handling.
Maintain type of end event if a message is stored in the dead letter queue. You can choose between Escalated and Completed.
Change the prefix if you like to setup an additional pipeline.
Switch parameter to false if you like to use the so called tilde option to determine the partner ID (not recommended).
Set parameter to true if you like to use custom exit across all scenarios.
Maintain ProcessDirect end point of global custom exit flow if you like to use custom exit across all scenarios.
